{"tid":1941011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超突發》支那「商人」入境香港 免14日隔離","createTime":"2020-03-24T07:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T08:26:28.000Z","uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3b3558d2d586b8a7e1f893e3e497c14f66af3872","tid":1941011,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb21c70068db873e1fa0f7228a4e97e5ad95d67","tid":1941011,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:07:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100003868649005/posts/1607643309374608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100003868649005%2Fposts%2F1607643309374608&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=f7d18761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100003868649005/posts/1607643309374608</a>"},{"pid":"ce053a2da65d21e0fab9c7252739a9fcde028343","tid":1941011,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"政府疑給商家優待，往返中港豁免隔離<br />\n<br />\n＊　＊　＊<br />\n<br />\n先後有兩名知情人披露，政府向各大商會提供《豁免強制檢疫申請書》，允許往返中港的廠商乃至其司機均享豁免，赴內地返港後毋須強制檢疫隔離 14 日。然而政府從未向外公布詳情。<br />\n<br />\n現時已從世界各地到港的人皆須接受強制檢疫隔離 14 日，從大陸回來的港人亦須家居隔離 14 日，期間不得出門（<a href=\"http://cutt.ly/dtvKoGN）。唯有八項要務獲許豁免。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcutt.ly%2FdtvKoGN%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%E5%94%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%85%AB%E9%A0%85%E8%A6%81%E5%8B%99%E7%8D%B2%E8%A8%B1%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E3%80%82&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=aa928eef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cutt.ly/dtvKoGN）。唯有八項要務獲許豁免。</a><br />\n<br />\n然而一名在某商會工作的 A 女士披露，商會向成員發出通告，謂「國內疫情正有逐步減退現象」，故「頻繁來往兩地的企業高管或技術人員」可向政府申請豁免，由工業貿易署負責審批（圖 1-2）。<br />\n<br />\n儘管政府公報嘗言，為香港提供「日常生活的物品或服務的人士」方准豁免檢疫（<a href=\"http://cutt.ly/KtvJwGl），但從申請文件可見（圖\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcutt.ly%2FKtvJwGl%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E5%BE%9E%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%AF%E8%A6%8B%EF%BC%88%E5%9C%96&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=d8e75eff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cutt.ly/KtvJwGl），但從申請文件可見（圖</a> 3-4）不止廠商其人，只要填報由司機駕車，連司機也可一併申請豁免。<br />\n<br />\n另一知情者 B 女士披露，有些廠商將申請表給予下屬，要求他們申請豁免，代為返大陸處理業務。據知那些企業皆非生產生活必需品。<br />\n<br />\n筆者兩度致電工業貿易署，兩名職員均答《豁免申請書》屬實，但申請人數太多，正在分流，未能確定何時獲批。<br />\n<br />\n筆者聲稱從事手機殼生產，有沒有資格申請。職員答申請者須要在大陸設廠，並須符合前述「日常生活所需」之要求（圖 5），最後交由主任決定。"},{"pid":"7a8f5495456df0fba38e9bfdd34139a7a973cd98","tid":1941011,"uid":76365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:10:20.000Z","msg":"司機就勉強話可以，因為下下十四日隔離邊有咁多司機揸車運貨<br />\n但商人都比?係咪on9?"},{"pid":"92bdb3da5501c2b1af5a0bf1d20fb464f223cd54","tid":1941011,"uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"做生意=疫苗=唔會病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316f1006ce4692ad884b70c4ec7b004891e8ffb9","tid":1941011,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54477de9b7c188f3f8816679cc5afa273b18ec27","tid":1941011,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a8f5495456df0fba38e9bfdd34139a7a973cd98","tid":1941011,"uid":76365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:10:20.000Z","msg":"司機就勉強話可以，因為下下十四日隔離邊有咁多司機揸車運貨<br />\n但商人都比?係咪on9?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"中港貨車佬一開始已經豁免，而家係講緊老闆車果個司機"},{"pid":"29509e4fc1fd7d88a9e11d83abf568e94d43aa26","tid":1941011,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"唔放點洗黑錢同放武警入關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0cc50a199ab6cf5f1c362b6fcae13b79edf59d","tid":1941011,"uid":293921,"